SUMMARY:Sturtevant Ravine Work Party!
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Sturtevant Ravine. \nHelp continue forest restoration at the Ravine! We will be planting bare root plants and plugs along with clearing out blackberry and other plants that are surrounding native plants that need our support. \nRegister
