SUMMARY:Spring Planting - Community Event at Lincoln Park
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Lincoln Park. \nHooray for Spring and Spring Planting! We’ll be installing native bare root plants and trees in a beautiful area of urban forest in the Park. We promise you lots of good nature vibes and high fives. Please be sure that all volunteers\, including youth are registered! Bare Root Planting 101 Video: click here \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/spring-planting-community-event-at-lincoln-park/
LOCATION:Lincoln Park\, 8011 Fauntleroy Wy SW\, Seattle\, WA\, 98136\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/spring-planting-community-event-at-lincoln-park_2991-ywkh4t.jpg
END:VEVENT
