SUMMARY:Longfellow Creek GS Restoration Event
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Longfellow Creek GS: Yancy. \nDelridge Neighborhoods Development Association offers twice-weekly opportunities for hands-on volunteering outdoors in the forests of West Seattle. Volunteers work to support our mission\, values\, history and commitment to social justice in the Delridge neighborhood. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/longfellow-creek-gs-restoration-event-37/
