SUMMARY:MUCC Work Party at Magnolia Park
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Magnolia Park. \nThere is work to be done to reclaim Magnolia Park S.E. Forest in Magnolia Park. Non-native plants have taken over\, and volunteers are needed to help defend this beautiful natural area. Join neighbors and friends to help out and learn about how we plan on bringing this forest back to a natural environment. \nRegister \nLearn more about Golden Gardens Park here.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/mucc-work-party-march-8th/
LOCATION:Magnolia Park\, 1461 Magnolia Blvd. W\, Seattle\, WA\, 98199\, United States
