SUMMARY:It's Friday the 13th for the Non-native Grasses in our Pollinator Patch
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Burke-Gilman Trail. \nWe’ll be removing Non-native grasses et al in this section of our Pollinator Patch to save our native wild flowers from being squeezed out. \nRegister to meet.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/its-friday-the-13th-for-the-non-native-grasses-in-our-pollinator-patch/
